{"tid":1798771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CNN公布五位亞洲推動變革年輕領袖　港候任區議員仇栩欣入選","createTime":"2019-12-26T12:45:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T06:34:12.000Z","uid":81228,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d326865ff20b806f93b804f91448d485ff012d6d","tid":1798771,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:45:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191226/_2019122616175932027.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191226%2F_2019122616175932027.jpg&h=762d453c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCNN最新公布五位亞洲推動變革年輕領袖，右一的香港候任東區區議員仇栩欣入選。（CNN圖片）<br />\n<br />\n據美國有線電視新聞網（CNN）報道，2019年全球各地的學生和年輕人，為推動性別平等和氣候行動等社會議題而努力。CNN最新公布了五位亞洲推動變革的年輕領袖，其中香港候任東區區議員仇栩欣榜上有名。<br />\n<br />\n報道指現年23歲的候任東區區議員的仇栩欣，受2014年的雨傘運動所覺悟，當年仍是學生的她，曾反問自己將來可用甚麼方式幫助社會，畢業後她先在一家銀行擔任客戶經理，其後參與反送中示威活動，她不忍心看到香港陷入危險，於是決定參選11月的區議會選舉。在競選拉票期間受襲受傷，後來她上載一條自己遭遇襲的影片到社交網站後，錄得83萬次瀏覽，最後她更成功擊敗連任的對手獲選為東區區議員，盼為市民發聲，守護香港的民主自由。<br />\n<br />\n其他入選的亞洲年輕領袖包括台灣「婚姻平權大平台」成員翁鈺清、印度年輕環保運動家柏迪（Ridhima Pandey）、南韓女權運動者Jijie Yang，以及緬甸倡導言論自由組織Athan共同創辦人之一的Ye Wai Phyo Aung。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1667880/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-CNN%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E4%BA%94%E4%BD%8D%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E8%AE%8A%E9%9D%A9%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E9%A0%98%E8%A2%96-%E6%B8%AF%E5%80%99%E4%BB%BB%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E4%BB%87%E6%A0%A9%E6%AC%A3%E5%85%A5%E9%81%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1667880%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-CNN%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B8%2583%25E4%25BA%2594%25E4%25BD%258D%25E4%25BA%259E%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%25AE%258A%25E9%259D%25A9%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25BC%2595%25E9%25A0%2598%25E8%25A2%2596-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2580%2599%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E4%25BB%2587%25E6%25A0%25A9%25E6%25AC%25A3%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%2581%25B8&d=xSG8yb8yy9PjQoJ4RYEJZFSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=ed976204\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1667880%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-CNN%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B8%2583%25E4%25BA%2594%25E4%25BD%258D%25E4%25BA%259E%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%25AE%258A%25E9%259D%25A9%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25BC%2595%25E9%25A0%2598%25E8%25A2%2596-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2580%2599%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E4%25BB%2587%25E6%25A0%25A9%25E6%25AC%25A3%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%2581%25B8&h=bf70c9a1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1667880/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-CNN%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E4%BA%94%E4%BD%8D%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E8%AE%8A%E9%9D%A9%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E9%A0%98%E8%A2%96-%E6%B8%AF%E5%80%99%E4%BB%BB%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E4%BB%87%E6%A0%A9%E6%AC%A3%E5%85%A5%E9%81%B8</a>"},{"pid":"051111bc2a5fd7a4bf18460953175b7ea64b2bf5","tid":1798771,"uid":35378,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:47:20.000Z","msg":"唔係話乜<br />\n<br />\n拍落去其他幾個侯選人差緊d喎"},{"pid":"952028430c8b688fe68f3fd1840b9a4f7bdb0b51","tid":1798771,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:47:35.000Z","msg":"可惜已經上過蘋果/民主黨d活動<br />\n<br />\n下屆多數輸番<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />路自己簡"},{"pid":"6166c47b3faf1890c06ec961d5227dd7c3efbc33","tid":1798771,"uid":317979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:48:50.000Z","msg":"仲以為全部都係女<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f3dd60b0af4b169d882005594b936afe8674a1a","tid":1798771,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:53:47.000Z","msg":"點解唔係gphone周庭, 反而係佢<img src=